## Component Principles

All Bioma components follow these principles:

- **Accessible**: WCAG AA compliant with proper ARIA labels
- **Token-Based**: Use design tokens exclusively (no hardcoded values)
- **Standalone**: Angular standalone components for better tree-shaking
- **Typed**: Full TypeScript support with strict types
- **Documented**: Comprehensive Storybook documentation

